name: REMOTE (person person couch person)
description:
An original Gory Orgy animated loop. 23 seconds. 1228X1228, H264, 2021
REMOTE is a multi-layered animation that utilises more than one machine-learning model. A fleshy, shape-shifting tangle (computer generated erotica) is conspicuously analysed by a machine-learning model that identifies people and objects. REMOTE (person person couch person) is one of a pair. One copy is retained by the artist, while the other is available for purchase. Gory Orgy is the experimental machine-learning project by kiwi artist and film-maker Ed Lust.
